"Diet Windows95"

This piece was super fun to make; I'm a huge fan of Microsoft aesthetic and wanted to honor it in this iteration. I made sure to research each element and the visual history of Window95 to create this as authentically as possible. Made on ASUS Zenbook S16.

@stevedv.eth I appreciate you for dueling, I have a lot of respect for you, so this is very meaningful. I know you aren't a huge fan of soda or windows, but you did great & are a huge part of why this was so fun!

@blankspace thank you for consistently bringing taste to the timeline and hosting this duel!

how it was made: This was made fully using Adobe illustrator+photoshop. lmk if any of you would be interested in a workflow / behind the scenes video!
